  unstable 1.5.18 1.4.2.3
    stable        1.4.2.3 1.4.2.2i 1.4.2.1i 1.4.2i
    secure        1.4.2.3
  optional openssl --with-ssl '' to enable ssl support for pop/imap
  category network/email
 attribute client console
  homepage http://www.mutt.org/
       url 'ftp://ftp.mutt.org/mutt/
            ftp://ftp.mutt.org/mutt/devel/
